title: 09/27: Start or Sit (AFC); Big Fantasy Questions! (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
Starting the show with some intriguing Fantasy questions as we assess the values of Sony Michel (2:48), Mark Ingram (4:48), Jameis Winston (6:15), Matt Breida (6:51) and more ... All the latest news (10:30) including an update on Le'Veon Bell, Dalvin Cook, A.J. Green, Alshon Jeffery and injuries to offensive linemen and defensive players that could have an impact this week ... HOU-IND (24:40), CLE-OAK (32:55), MIA-NE (36:15), NYJ-JAC (44:00), PHI-TEN (46:42), KC-DEN (50:45), SF-LAC (56:10), BAL-PIT (1:00:30) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
